{"tid":1238993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"魯比奧提出修正案　阻華為在專利法院尋求索償","createTime":"2019-06-18T04:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T03:45:59.000Z","uid":141151,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"65bd64ba3533d1d83d69f0201048c3463cc44cf0","tid":1238993,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:19:41.000Z","msg":"魯比奧提出修正案　阻華為在專利法院尋求索償<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190618/bkn-20190618041055486-0618_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190618%2Fbkn-20190618041055486-0618_00972_001.html&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXjcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=21a67dde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190618/bkn-20190618041055486-0618_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國參議員魯比奧周一（17日）提出修正案，阻止中國科技巨企華為向美國專利法院尋求賠償。根據有關文件，在美國觀察名單上包括華為在內的部分企業，將被禁止在美國法律下就美國的專利尋求索償，包括就破壞專利指控入稟法院。 <br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒引述消息指，華為上周三（12日）向美國電訊公司維里佐通訊索取牌照費10億美元（約78億港元），當中涉及華為超過230項專利。報道相信這是華為抵抗美國政府封殺所採取的新策略。 <br />\n<br />\n魯比奧提出的是《美國國防授權法》（NDAA）的修正案，NDAA主宰了國防部每年的預算、支出和政策。"},{"pid":"7d9c493e469b9545e5c353a7547e74383b2d027e","tid":1238993,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:25:14.000Z","msg":"Rubio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49aac5ef50a0aea6aae39a6d66e9dd8d86eb7645","tid":1238993,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f3fec60cbdc83bc985f651194eb96dc05b4d64","tid":1238993,"uid":188176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"大陸玩慣球證旁證都係我d人<br />\n而家比人玩番個感覺係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7489b7466dd5d5a517eb05eb90242622f2d950e2","tid":1238993,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b88eaa00121b640324054bad204e78edcd2419e","tid":1238993,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd1a9fcabd0c78ce4d47e6e124f0a170056b4f6","tid":1238993,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}